{"tid":1740414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全國人大：香港暴力活動升級與「美國國會」插手相關","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T03:41:56.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"556354d6ea433711592d0d836d15eb34978511d2","tid":1740414,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493397-20191120.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493397-20191120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=528aa541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493397-20191120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=98fd2d11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493397-20191120.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n 全國人大外委會：香港暴力活動升級與美國國會插手相關<br />\n2019-11-20 HKT 10:21<br />\n分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n<br />\n全國人大外事委員會就美國國會參議院通過「香港人權與民主法案」發表聲明，表示堅決反對和強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，五個多月來香港發生的一系列危害公共安全和公共秩序的暴力犯罪，嚴重踐踏法治和社會秩序，嚴重破壞香港的繁榮穩定，嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」原則底線。近來，香港暴力分子的打砸燒破壞活動不斷升級，甚至殘害普通市民，毫無行為底線、人性道德、法律戒懼，這與美國國會插手香港事務、干涉中國內政是密切相關。<br />\n<br />\n聲明強調，止暴制亂、恢復秩序是香港當前最緊迫的任務，是香港社會的最廣泛民意和最大人權。美國參議院在極少數反華議員的鼓噪下，不但不譴責令人髮指的暴力犯罪，反而借「人權」、「民主」之名繼續為暴力分子撐腰打氣，充分暴露了美國國會在人權和民主問題上的極端虛偽、赤裸裸的雙重標準以及反中亂港的險惡用心。<br />\n<br />\n聲明重申，維護國家主權、安全、發展利益是全面準確貫徹「一國兩制」方針的必然要求。香港事務是中國的內政，香港事務必須在中華人民共和國憲法和香港特別行政區基本法的框架內處理。香港是中國的香港，任何外部勢力不得干涉。"},{"pid":"f91280ba60f0c2a76bd83a59df35e14efd837253","tid":1740414,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明「香港人權與民主法案」完全正確"},{"pid":"55ff99549841879712053e4860cb256f69cbfb35","tid":1740414,"uid":146030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:27:56.000Z","msg":"睇嚟支那都決心攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf8e7207e98c5bad50de14c69de53b72344b7b4","tid":1740414,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899d38008065f876927846294ca21aec9fc9ff3a","tid":1740414,"uid":55955,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"本來唔知有冇用<br />\n見到咁多聲明，我就知做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999097c54951ede62613343d8cd9be499675fe98","tid":1740414,"uid":69761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"要堅持<br />\n要商家周圍都做唔到生意<br />\n聖誕冇生意<br />\n新年冇生意<br />\n攬抄"},{"pid":"041269b5821f599003602f9ee43e0470a83bc296","tid":1740414,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135ac3a4bef065cf81076415ecf6d619f4267144","tid":1740414,"uid":126115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"極少數反華議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b801ed0fcc1749cab4774d0fc11d441d1b72ca","tid":1740414,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"135ac3a4bef065cf81076415ecf6d619f4267144","tid":1740414,"uid":126115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:29:14.000Z","msg":"極少數反華議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"法案係參議院全票通過.."},{"pid":"552de301dbe5a1022a146bbaa7ad0cf852989266","tid":1740414,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"唔樂觀 <br />\n好擔心會加强打壓<br />\n大家小心"},{"pid":"add43acc94295c7ff9a733570d1b4006056795a4","tid":1740414,"uid":261913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT